data.eml:eml: New records of bathyal Leptolida (Cnidaria: Hydrozoa: Leptothecata) from the Bay of Biscay and the northwestern Iberian Peninsula (northeastern Atlantic)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Altuna, Álvaro (2012): New records of bathyal Leptolida (Cnidaria: Hydrozoa: Leptothecata) from the Bay of Biscay and the northwestern Iberian Peninsula (northeastern Atlantic). Zootaxa 3565: 1-17, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.211232
